      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PYRENEES PIZAZZ (1) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at this track over 410m behind Paw Farina (23.75) in a Grade 5. The form from his last run stacks up well. Better than last start and worth following up. GUITAR TANGO (6) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (23.71) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Key player on best and worth another try. PAW LAMPADES (4) box seated before sticking on well to finish 8 lengths away in second (27.51) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 485m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Will give a great sight again. WINNING STEPS (2) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
